### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = seu_jwt_token_aqui

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Obter usuário atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}} 